Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${perl:Depends}, hunspell, chktex, languagetool
Description: Comprehensive checker for texts written in (La)Tex.
  Mainly focused on checking MSc theses
  and scientific papers. Autozoil has
  been used for Polish and English
  texts so far. The program was created
  for checking MSc theses supervised by
  Filip Grali≈Ñski at the Faculty of Mathematics
  and Computer Science of Adam
  Mickiewicz University in 2010/2011.
